The program will stimulate a rolling dice game
The program consists of 3 files:
1. player_class.py
contains the Player class
2. game_class.py
contains the Game class
3. main.py
execution

To run the program, save 3 files in the same folder.
Run the main file.
Or if you want to run them in the terminal
usage: python3 main.py <length> <number of player>
